    title: 'I Don\'t Want to Be a "Rose Boy"',
    subtitle: 'The "Privilege" of a Transgender Man in China',
    excerpt: 'A transgender man\'s journey through medical transition and the memory of a friend lost to suicide.',
    date: 'April 19, 2023',
    readTime: '12 min read',
    tags: ['Gender', 'Identity'],
    customImages: ['/images/rose-boy.jpg'],
